{"lastModified":1776325001664,"uri":"c::9938368400::vessel::c854a3c0-3a20-11f0-b55b-e5b737adbb05","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area:\nSummer 2026: Corsica, French Riviera & Monaco, Italy - Sardinia\nWinter 2025/2026: British Virgin Islands, Leeward Islands, Windward Islands\n\nAHAVA is a masterpiece of luxury and design, offering an extraordinary charter experience defined by elegance, comfort, and sophistication. The yacht’s beautifully curated interiors feature fine walnut wood paneling, plush designer furnishings, and a collection of exceptional art pieces by renowned artists such as Alex Katz, Julian Opie, and Christopher Kieling. These remarkable pieces perfectly complement the yacht’s sophisticated, contemporary design, transforming every space into a floating gallery.\n\nThe expansive main saloon is designed for both entertainment and relaxation, with a refined dining area, a state-of-the-art barista station, and an inviting lounge with panoramic views. The master suite is a serene retreat, boasting a king-sized bed, a spa-inspired en-suite bathroom, and a private Hammam for ultimate rejuvenation.\n\nOutdoor living is equally impressive, with a spacious flybridge featuring a hammock chair, custom dining tables, and a bar—ideal for sunset cocktails. The aft deck offers elegant seating and ample space for alfresco dining and social gatherings. Guests can enjoy both indoor and outdoor cinema setups, with the option of watching films in the luxurious comfort of the main saloon or under the stars on the aft deck. Whether indulging in watersports, exploring on e-bikes, or enjoying an open-air movie night, AHAVA delivers an unparalleled luxury charter experience.","blueprint":{"name":"AHAVA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::c854a3c0-3a20-11f0-b55b-e5b737adbb05::assets::60139f30-45f8-11f0-aeda-a71754925eac/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::c854a3c0-3a20-11f0-b55b-e5b737adbb05::assets::c4d14201-3a23-11f0-bcce-11